@node Main "Roman_Wheel - Documentation"

                            'Roman_Wheel' 1.02

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'Roman_Wheel' is a Workbench @{" game " link play} where the game board is in the form of
a wheel containing 8 positions that surround a central position, the central
position is linked to 4 of the positions in the wheel. You have to place the
numbers from 1 to 8 in the wheel and they must be put clockwise.

  Have fun!

