@node play "The game: Installation/Playing"

                             Installation

  The installation is very simple, just place "Roman_Wheel" where you
want on your hard drive, floppy disk, Ram Disk, etc. No other files or
Libraries are needed.

                             How to play?

  To play, click on a position occupied by a number that is linked
to the empty space, this will move the number to that empty space.
Try to complete the game in the minimum of moves possible.

  When all the numbers are placed in the right order and the central
space is empty, the game ends and it will display the number of moves
you have made.

  Have fun!

@{b}OPTIONS@{ub}

  In the game window, the following buttons are shown:

-New Game            -Restarts the game.

-About               -Displays the informations about 'Roman_Wheel'.

@endnode

